\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf10 Evan }{\f8\fs26\b0\i1\cf11 (irritated)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf10 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf12 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93Come on Liz, I told you hundred times I\u8217\'92m fine. I told you, my employer requires that I get a physical every six months. I have another fiscal coming up after the new year.\u8221\'94}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0   }
