\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0 Evan got up and rinsed off his plate unloaded in the dishwasher hoping to distract the conversation.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf10 Evan }{\f8\fs26\b0\i1\cf11 (frustrated)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf10 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf12 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93They\u8217\'92re thorough enough mom. You think the fitness club would let me work there if I had even a hint of an issue? I rarely get those anymore.\u8221\'94}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0   }
