\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf10 Liz:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf12 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93Sarah, have you seen Evan experience walls and energy.\u8221\'94}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0   }
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf10 Sarah }{\f8\fs26\b0\i1\cf11 (helpful and sincere)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf10 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf12 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93Evan has more energy than any human being I\u8217\'92ve ever met. It\u8217\'92s a constant struggle to get him to sit down for an hour while were studying. I thought he would take a break after softball season ended, but now basketball twice a week in addition to his regular workouts, in addition to the volunteer work he does with me. Honestly, I don\u8217\'92t know how he does it.\u8221\'94}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0   }
\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0 Evan\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s smiled widely. He thought to himself finally someone on his side regarding this issue.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf10 Evan }{\f8\fs26\b0\i1\cf11 (feeling he had been validated)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf10 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf12 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93See Liz. I told you I\u8217\'92m fine. Sarah would know better than anybody.\u8221\'94}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }
\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0 Unfortunately for Evan, Sarah wasn\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92t finished.}
