\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf10 Sarah}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf10 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf12 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93That is true. That\u8217\'92s why I\u8217\'92ve never worried about it, before.\u8221\'94}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0   }
